name: NIKE BOT
description:
Yup that's right, the reason why you wake up early on Saturday mornings and aren't able to get any of the releases you want. Forget the resellers, forget the hype, forget paying extra for something you shouldn't have to. This Nike twitter bot has successfully gotten many sneakers releases, including limited releases such as the LeBron X Corks and the LeBron X Denims!!! 

Now you may be asking yourself, 

How does this work?
Well I'll tell you how right here.
This bot is very easy and simple to use and also set up. All you have to do is set up the bot and wake up a few minutes before the 8:00AM release and sign into twitter. That simple, the bot does everything else for you. The bot will constantly refresh your twitter feed and look for the keyword of the release that you give it, once the tweet pops up on your newsfeed it will instantly click the release link and add the size you want and sneakers to your cart in a matter of a second or 2. This is the best bot and it doesn't cost much either. It will payback within its first use.

What do I need to use this?
A PC or MAC, and also Google Chrome. 

How do I set it up?
An instructional video will be sent with the download and other instructions will be in the file too.

What will I be receiving?
You will be receiving 2 bots, a twitter scanner/link clicker bot and an auto add to cart bot, which together are unstoppable. You will also be receiving an instructional video on how to set up the bot.

How will I receive the bot?
I will send you a link to a download with the instructional video through your email address or facebook messages. 

How long until after I purchase will you send the bot?
Usually within the hour. I'm usually very fast with this.

Is it hard to set up the bot?
Not at all if you follow the detailed instructional video. Take very little time to set up.
